channel.title: What is one genre that it would be super-frustrating for you to make?
channel.description: This could be any genre - metal, orchestra, anything! The genre that would be hard for me is Metal, cause 1. I don’t know how to shake my head up and down and not get a headache, and 2. I don’t understand the circumstances of playing a guitar. Let me hear your opinion!
